description:
The Maestros of the 5th Łódź Tango Salon Festival 2015 dance “Gallo ciego” by La Juan D'Arienzo.

The Maestros are
Karina Colmeiro and Maximiliano Cristiani
María Inés Bogado and Sebastián Jiménez
Roxana Suárez and Sebastián Achával
Josefina Bermudez Avila and Fabián Peralta

If you love Tango videos, help us create more on
http://www.patreon.com/030tango

Łódź Tango Salon Festival
http://tangosalon.pl

http://www.030tango.com

Recorded on 2015/09/27
